  <summary date="2023-04-24T21:20:52Z" status="Introduced in House">Universal Full-Day Kindergarten Act

This bill requires the Department of Education to make formula grants to states and, through them, allocations to local educational agencies to carry out full-day kindergarten programs. ED must also reserve funds for outlying areas and the Bureau of Indian Education.</summary>
